<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DSA 90 Days Challenge</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #212529;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #343a40;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 32px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .description {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #495057;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: #0069d9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #6c757d;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #5a6268;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: #28a745;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #218838;
        }
        .feature {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 30px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .feature h3 {
            color: #343a40;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>90 Days DSA Challenge</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Master Data Structures & Algorithms with JavaScript</div>
        
        <p class="description">
            This application provides a comprehensive 90-day Data Structures and Algorithms challenge 
            designed to help you build strong programming fundamentals. Browse questions day by day, 
            view them in your browser, or download the complete guide as a PDF.
        </p>
        
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>ðŸš€ Key Features:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>90 days of carefully curated DSA problems</li>
                <li>Browse questions by day</li>
                <li>View all content directly in your browser</li>
                <li>Download the complete guide as a PDF</li>
                <li>Perfect for interview preparation</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="/dsa" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Questions</a>
            <a href="/view-pdf" class="btn" target="_blank">View PDF</a>
            <a href="/download-pdf" class="btn btn-secondary">Download PDF</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>